data.title: Cynthia Boyd Stone McDougal (1926
data.meta_description: Miss Cynthia Stone, wife of actor Jack Lemmon & Cliff Robertson, died from Cancer on 12-26-1988 in Miami Beach, Florida.  She is the daughter of Mr & Mrs. John Boyd Stone of Moss Avenue in Peoria, Illinois, and is a 1944 graduate of Peoria H.S., and the wife of Mr. John Uhler Jack Lemmon III, whom she married in Peoria...
